    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is transmitted via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is excellent, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings for optimal kinematic response. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing replacement, ensuring this high-revving powerhouse remains mechanically robust for its next enthusiast owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
