      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and long-term care. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, showing only the minor, negligible signs of road use typical for a well-loved car. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free environment where the premium materials have been preserved beautifully; the seats are supportive and free of significant wear, and all interior electronics\u2014including the navigation and premium audio system\u2014function exactly as they did on day one. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, backed by a comprehensive service history that proves it has never missed an oil change. The transmission shifts are seamless, and the suspension remains tight and responsive, providing a smooth ride over any surface. With four matching tires featuring deep tread and a fresh brake service just completed, this car is completely turn-key and ready for its next chapter.",
